About us

Delivering the disruptive potential of quantum computing

Founded in 2019, Aegiq is a UK based full-stack photonic quantum computing company. We work with customers in a wide range of industries, including defence, aerospace, cybersecurity and AI, to solve their most demanding computational challenges.

What we do

Comprehensive end-user solutions designed for ease of use

Component modules

Proprietary photonic microchips from our patented single photon source technology to our switching and quantum processing units.

Hardware systems

Fastest clock speeds for solving problems beyond classical computers’ reach using photons. Datacentre compatible in standard racks.

Quantum software

Solution development to maximise customer value, whether it’s optimisation, quantum simulation, or data analytics.

Products

Powerful quantum platform for a new era of computing

Aegiq’s integrated photonic approach offers speed, compactness and modularity with a clear path towards the fault tolerant era of large scale quantum computers.
Artemis. Photonic quantum computer
Reconfigurable system for deployment and implementation of photonic-based quantum computing in analog and gate-based modes.

Key features

Hybrid
Modular photonic integrated circuits interfaced with optical fibre leveraging the best of silicon based photonic platforms and compound semiconductors
Manufacturability
High-volume foundry semiconductor manufacturing
Connectivity
Modular interconnectivity using standard telecom optical fibre
Robustness
Mild cooling allowing simple integration into standard environments
Speed
Fastest modality clock cycles to achieve commercial advantage faster
